      "texts": [
        {"text": "核心问题：三个必须回答的拷问", "x": 0.8, "y": 0.15, "w": 11.73, "h": 0.7, "fontSize": 28, "bold": true, "color": "#B89A6A", "font": "Microsoft YaHei"},
        {"text": "01", "x": 0.9, "y": 1.8, "w": 1, "h": 0.6, "fontSize": 28, "bold": true, "color": "#C00000", "font": "Franklin Gothic Medium"},
        {"text": "谁买单？", "x": 0.9, "y": 2.4, "w": 3.2, "h": 0.6, "fontSize": 22, "bold": true, "color": "#B89A6A", "font": "Microsoft YaHei"},
        {"text": "最终付费方是谁？\n产业链各环节的真实支付意愿如何？\n算力用户 vs 数据中心 vs 电网/政府——三个层次的付费动机完全不同。", "x": 0.9, "y": 3.1, "w": 3.2, "h": 3.0, "fontSize": 14, "color": "#FFFFFF", "font": "Microsoft YaHei"},
        {"text": "02", "x": 5.09, "y": 1.8, "w": 1, "h": 0.6, "fontSize": 28, "bold": true, "color": "#C00000", "font": "Franklin Gothic Medium"},
        {"text": "数据在哪？", "x": 5.09, "y": 2.4, "w": 3.2, "h": 0.6, "fontSize": 22, "bold": true, "color": "#B89A6A", "font": "Microsoft YaHei"},
        {"text": "没有真实交易数据的AI平台没有护城河。\n电力交易数据高度敏感，电网公司不会轻易开放。\n能跑通实盘才是真壁垒。", "x": 5.09, "y": 3.1, "w": 3.2, "h": 3.0, "fontSize": 14, "color": "#FFFFFF", "font": "Microsoft YaHei"},
        {"text": "03", "x": 9.28, "y": 1.8, "w": 1, "h": 0.6, "fontSize": 28, "bold": true, "color": "#C00000", "font": "Franklin Gothic Medium"},
        {"text": "为什么是你？", "x": 9.28, "y": 2.4, "w": 3.2, "h": 0.6, "fontSize": 22, "bold": true, "color": "#B89A6A", "font": "Microsoft YaHei"},
        {"text": "电力行业极度排外。\n跨界团队必须回答：凭什么电网选你而不是体系内供应商？\n如果答案是\"因为我们AI更厉害\"，大概率没想清楚。", "x": 9.28, "y": 3.1, "w": 3.2, "h": 3.0, "fontSize": 14, "color": "#FFFFFF", "font": "Microsoft YaHei"}
